title: Aleksandar Nedeljković
text:
Aleksandar Nedeljkovic (born April 14, 1982) is a <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>n <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player, who currently plays for SC Gradisce.
Career.
He played in the <a href="Serbian%20First%20League">Serbian First League</a> for <a href="FK%20Zemun">FK Zemun</a> and Zmaj Zemun. He joined in summer 2007 to German lower club FC Drita Kosova Kornwestheim and played since 2009 in Austria. First time presented until summer 2011 <a href="SV%20Aspern">SV Aspern</a> and since them for SC Gradisce Vienna.
